{"tid":221890,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"王振民指若兩制威脅一國安全將無法繼續","createTime":"2017-04-29T05:37:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-29T08:02:39.000Z","uid":30561,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2bafa2399118b861606c1e4c4ada551e01d25b0d","tid":221890,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T05:37:40.000Z","msg":"中聯辦法律部部長王振民指，如果有人以兩制為藉口鬧獨立，威脅一國的安全，任何國家都無法繼續兩制的安排。王振民在一個基本法研討會上致辭，指現在有人想把香港從國家分裂出去，得寸進尺，把中央逼到牆角，甚至有港獨人士進入建制和學校，令國家感到非常寒心。他指中央好心好意給香港維持兩制、高度自治，若果這安排令國家感到很大麻煩，成為一國的障礙阻力，甚至威脅國家的存在，任何國家都無法繼續兩制的安排。"},{"pid":"53fda60a745445a21ef8faf8e043cbaf08e97ec2","tid":221890,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T06:07:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f1111a55251f9b17ca5e9b3854bdb6c8ca69bdf","tid":221890,"uid":69895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T06:21:44.000Z","msg":"你老母，而家就係要一國一制，香港泥民已經無野輸。"},{"pid":"b83ea1675eb2d455e8f54ccbd504c5d9b5b81e76","tid":221890,"uid":42815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T06:34:37.000Z","msg":"迫到牆角，屌，香港人就真係比隻狼迫到牆角了；又無得安居，如果個個都安居樂業，邊個得閒同你大陸對着幹。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5a3e8626e0b56d9a67bca7106f3ed5efa1951a4","tid":221890,"uid":4964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T06:38:02.000Z","msg":"香港人自己話唔夠打，對方咪一樣吹到可以威脅&quot;一國&quot;存在<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2c5b8f60703cd37930c5393027fcd16e3fd88ce","tid":221890,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T07:25:30.000Z","msg":"大部分港人一點反應都冇"},{"pid":"a5319ddf86a4e57a3485ed53789d9a85b3d30b7b","tid":221890,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T08:02:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}